==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Yankee-Doodle
<hw>Yan`kee-Doo"dle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The name of a tune adopted popularly as one of the national airs of
the United States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Humorously, a Yankee.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>We might have withheld our political noodles⟦br⟧
From knocking their heads against hot <qex>Yankee-Doodles</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Moore.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yankeeism</ent>⟦br⟧
